Dialogs.Dialog: Phew, I'm done with my work today...
Ah, a message...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ sent me a message？ She's just left. I wonder if she forgot something here.
"Please come to the school's backyard. - Nene."
(She sent me a message asking me to meet her...)
(But why at school...？)
(In the backyard...)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！
姉ヶ崎
What's the matter？ Why did you message me all of a sudden？ And why at school...？
Well, I was thinking that Dixie's might be okay, but...
Supposing... Just supposing that we were in the same grade...
We could have met at school...
And we could have spent most of our time together at school...
When I thought about that, I just chose this place without realizing...
Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
Yes, I made a mistake by entering Dixie's from the front door...
Actually, I was thinking, "If this kid was such a burden like that, it might be hard for me to work with him."
Well, blame it on the nice Spring weather, hm？
It was really hot. And ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you were carrying a large bucket. You seemed to be working hard.
Hehe. And I was grumbling. It was really embarrassing that you heard it.
I'm not quite good at working under the heat...
It was on a cool day in the Fall. I was about to go to work and was surprised to meet such a beautiful girl.
Right, and you flattered me at the first moment we met. I was also surprised.
I didn't flatter you. And I told you that already.
That caused me some misunderstanding and I even doubted whether or not you would be a nice kid.
It was a very cold day. You were sweeping in front of the restaurant, right？
Yeah, that was such a painful work...
Actually, another staff member was absent on that day. That's why I had to sweep out there.
What I was thinking back then was that...
What？
...The new employee had arrived and I had to give him guidance. He happened to be a junior at my school, so...
He would surely rely on me a lot.
Did I trouble you？
No, you didn't. That was just the feeling I had back then. But...
But, I knew I was wrong. You've betrayed me.
I betrayed you？
Yes, you're still not quite reliable and you still act childish, but it's not just like that.
"You can rely on me." You're the kind of guy who said that to me.
I've told you before that I am not as strong as I look.
Yes...
I had a person that I liked.
He was an upperclassman. To be a girl that'd be suitable for him, I tried my best in everything...
As a result, I've become this reliable Nene-san that everyone knows.
But I'm not that reliable... I just want the person I love to like me.
I want the person I love to be by my side...
I... want you to be by my side...
I... love you...
I love you, too
Sorry
...Really？
Yes, I also want ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ to be by my side.
I want you to be my girlfriend.
I'm so happy...
Me, too...
Can I get closer to you？
I've always wanted to do this...
Can I kiss you...？
Yeah...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
Never mind... It's okay...
I'm sorry. Our kiss was like that...
We can make up for this later, right...？
I don't think of you that way...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I like you, but...
It's not the same feeling that you have for me, so...
No, don't worry... Thanks for hearing me out.
Sorry...
Don't apologize. I was the one that called you here.
But, what will we be after this...？
If possible, can I keep having this feeling toward you...？
I'll also continue liking ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ as my friend...
Thanks. I'll keep on loving you, even though my feelings for you are more than feelings for a friend...
I love you...
Phew, I've finished my work today...
Telephone... From ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Although she has just left...
Hello...
姉ヶ崎
Hello. Um...
(She called me out...)
(But, why at school？)
(In the backyard...)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！
▲主人公＊▲.
Why did you call to ask me out？
And, why at school？
Because... There were a lot things happened between us at Dixie's, but that's not what I want us to be.
Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
Ah... I went in Dixie's front door instead of employees' entrance...
Right. I doubted if I could train you. That clumsiness was because of Spring's joyful atmosphere, huh？
It was in the middle of the Summer. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was sweating while working hard on her job.
Geez, you should've forgotten about that embarrassing moment.
Embarrassing...？ I was just thinking that you were really working hard.
Really？ Then that's fine.
It was a cool day in the fall. I went to work and met a beautiful girl.
Geez, if you keep saying this kind of thing in front of women, you won't grow up to be a good man, you know？
"Keep saying"？ I had only said it once...
Hehe, just kidding.
It was on a very cold day. You were sweeping outside. It seemed like a tough job.
Yeah, it was so painful. My hands became all numb.
But actually, I was helping out because of an absent staff member...
At that time, I was a little depressed.
Eh？ Why？
Because there was a new employee that I had to train. To make the matter worse, he was my junior at my school...
Sorry...
Hehe. You don't have to apologize. I was just teasing you.
But he turned out to be interesting, so it was fine...
Interesting？
Right. He was a newcomer, and younger than me, yet he asked me to rely on him. Such a cheeky guy.
That was very interesting. I was really happy when he said that to me.
Really...？
I've told you before that I'm not as strong as I look.
Yes...
I had a person that I liked.
He was an upperclassman.
I always tried my very best just to be able to stand by his side.
That was the only reason...
To think back, I'm not sure if that was the right thing to do...
Now that I'm looking at you here, I really doubt that what I had always done might be wrong.
Look at how you've always tried your best... You're innocent, cute, and charming...
And, I have fallen in love with you...
...Will you become my boyfriend...？
I love you
Sorry
Eh？ Really...？
Yes... If you think I'm good enough for you, I want to be ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s boyfriend.
...Then I'll be your girlfriend, not your big sister, you know？
Yes, I know...
I see. Then from now on, you are my boyfriend.
...Hey, I'm going there.
O-Okay...
Hehe, isn't your heart throbbing？
That's right...
Don't you want to kiss？
That's...
I want to...
...What's wrong？
B-But...
Hey, stop speaking.
I wonder if you are...
Stop speaking...
I don't think of you like that...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I like you, but it's not the same feeling as what ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ has toward me...
So...
No, it's okay.
This is too bad, but it can't be helped...
Don't apologize anymore. One reason I love you is because you're like this...
Hey, from now on, you won't try to avoid me, right？
No, I won't.
Then that's fine...
Please continue to be nice to me, okay？
Phew, just a little bit more until today's job is done. I'll just hang in there！
姉ヶ崎
Hey.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... Did you finish your work early today？
Well...
(She said she had something to talk to me after I finished my work. What could it be...？)
(And, why at school...？)
(In the backyard, huh...？)
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！
▲主人公＊▲.
What's the matter？ Why did you want to talk to me？
And why not at Dixie's, but at school...？
Because we might be interrupted if we talked at Dixie's.
I wanted this to be private.
No, I mean, this is a very private business...
And What exactly is it...？
Hey, don't rush me...
While I was waiting for you, I thought about the first time we met.
Hey, do you still remember it？
I came to work at Dixie's but I entered from the front door...
Hehe, that's why I thought you were a customer.
The weather was kind of warm outside. Maybe you could blame it on that. Hehe.
It was such a hot day, but ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was working very hard.
That time... To tell you the truth...
It was really tough working like that and it was embarrassing that you saw me.
It was a cool day in the fall. I was really surprised when I saw the beautiful ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
You don't have to repeat that kind of flattery.
It's my honest opinion...
Geez, don't make me feel embarrassed.
You were sweeping outside on a very cold day.
That was really painful... I was thinking why I had to do it that day.
I was helping out because a staff member was absent, but that job was too much.
At that time, I didn't think that things would turn out this way...
...This way？
I had to train someone who was my junior at school. I was wondering if I could turn him into a reliable staff.
...Sorry that I turned out like this.
Hehe, don't worry. That part was something I had expected.
For a guy who couldn't even take care of his own job, it was cute when you told me that I could rely on you.
It's good if a newcomer can work on his own without my help, but with you, I felt different.
I want to continue taking care of you, and I don't want to part with you.
I've told you before that I am not as strong as I look.
Yes...
Well, I had someone that I loved...
He was an upperclassman.
I didn't want to rely on him too much, so I tried my best to act like an adult.
Even now that I've become like this, from his point of view, I'd still be just a cute underclassman to him.
But I don't care about that anymore.
Now that I've met you, you're just so cute. It really can't be helped.
You're so cute and I don't want to lose you... In other word... I love you.
I... want you to be my boyfriend.
I love you, too
Sorry...
Eh？ That's...
Yes, I love ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, too.
Really？ I don't want to be your big sister, you know？
I know. Not as an older sister, but as a woman.
I'm so happy... Can I go there...？
Hehe...
What？
Hey, I'll give you a kiss...
Eh？ Is that okay...？
Yes, I just want to do it.
...What？
Well...
Hehe, you want more？
No... Yes...
You can be honest...
I don't think of ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ that way...
I like you, but it's a different kind of feeling...
So...
Hah, as I thought...
An older girl is no good, huh？ So you like a girl in the same grade, or in a lower grade？
The age isn't the factor here...
But, you think of me as your big sister, right？
...Well, that's probably right...
I see. Then I think it's fine like this...
Will you let me be your big sister from now on...？
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
If you don't like it, I won't do it, but... From now on, can I call you by your first name？
Sure, that's fine
It's fine as it is
T-Thanks.
▲主人公＊▲. Please be nice to me...
Ah, okay. I see... I understand.
If you don't answer, it means okay, right？ I'll call you by your first name then.
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
Hey, I can call you by your first name from now on, right？
Sure, that's fine
It's fine as it is
Hehe, okay.
▲主人公＊▲. From now on please be nice to me, okay？
Eh？ Really？ Then I won't change how I call you. For now.
You didn't answer. Are you embarrassed？ Hehe, I'll call you by your first name then.
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
I'd be happy if I can call you by your first name from now on. How's that？
Sure, that's fine
It's fine as it is
Hehe. Yay！
▲主人公＊▲. Be nice to me, okay？
Too bad... But I understand. Then I won't change how I call you for now.
Eh？ What is it？ ...I'll just call you by your first name then, okay？
姉ヶ崎
If it doesn't trouble you, I wonder if we can go on a date this Sunday.
Okay, sounds good
I'll think about it
Really？ I'm so happy. It's a promise, okay？
I see... Too bad, but it can't be helped, huh？
As I thought... It troubled you, right？ I asked you too suddenly.
Ah, no. I spaced out for a bit. A date, right？ Okay！
Really？ I'm so glad...
姉ヶ崎
Hey, how about we go on a date this Sunday？
Okay, sounds good
I'll think about it
Hehe, nice reply. It's a promise, okay？
Hmm, I see. ...Fine, maybe next time.
Hey, are you listening？
Ah, no. I spaced out for a bit. A date, right？ Okay.
Geez, I thought I was turned down for a bit. Hehe.
姉ヶ崎
I was wondering if you would go on a date with me this Sunday...
Okay, sounds good
I'll think about it
Hehe, thanks.
Eh？ Really...？ Um, I understand. Maybe next time, okay？
...Is it inconvenient for you？
Sorry, I spaced out a bit. A date, right？ Okay.
Yay！ I'm glad. Then, you'll go with me, right？
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲. From now on... I'll be in your care.
Yeah, same here.
Bye-bye. I'll see you later.
Bye-bye. See you later.
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲. From now on, I'll be counting on you.
Yeah, same here.
Okay, bye-bye！
Bye-bye. I'll see you later.
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲. From now on, I'll be counting on you, okay？
Yeah, same here.
Bye-bye！ I'll see you later.
Bye-bye. See you later.
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
Thank you for being by my side...
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
We'll be together from now on. Are you ready for that？
姉ヶ崎
▲主人公＊▲.
From now on, we'll always be together.
